   * Infinity * x = Infinity for any finite positive x.
   * Infinity * x = -Infinity for any finite negative x.
   * -Infinity * x = -Infinity for any finite positive x.
   * -Infinity * x = Infinity for any finite negative x.
   * Infinity * 0 = NaN.
   * -Infinity * 0 = NaN.
